title: Premium Blended Charcoal Grey Kameez Shalwar/MKSHS10-Charcoal Grey
description:
Elevate Your Style: Premium Blended Kameez Shalwar
For the discerning gentleman who values both comfort and sophistication, look no further than WOV's Kameez Shalwar collection.
Crafted with premium blended viscose fabric, our Premium Blended Kameez Shalwar offers an unparalleled level of luxury and versatility. The smooth, silky feel caresses your skin, making it ideal for all-day wear, while the regular fit and matching buttons exude timeless elegance.
More than just everyday attire, these ensembles effortlessly transition from casual gatherings to evening events.

title: Dahlia Fields / LKD0768
description: A cotton net long coat style jacket with intricate floral embroidery hand embroidered with a multitude of coloured ribbon, crystal, pearl and kora that comes together to create a beautifully exclusive ensemble. Meticulously crafted, this boutique luxury retail design is paired harmoniously with a soft silken light lilac inner to enhance the exclusive ribbon work and shades of the blooms. Come join us in celebrating the new season and discover luxury retail like never before.

title: Malachite Allure 2Pc Set / LKH3109
description: This deep jade ensemble is the epitome of luxury and the highest standard in retail design. The gown features a bodice with an intricately hand embroidered neckline in kora french bullion, sequins, and resham silk thread. The flowing hem is encrusted with sequins and 3D detailing atop net lace and a scalloped hem.The flowing skirt is made of embroidered and sequined fabric aloft artisan jute latticework. The slit has a peekaboo insert of silken black material that adds layers of sophistication and amplifies the visual grandeur of the outfit and wearer. The gown is paired with a WOV signature classic cut cig pant in crushed silk with sequined detailing that can be seen on the sleeves as well.

title: Brunnera Thicket  2Pc Set/ LKPRM30
description: Join WOV on floral escapade with the newest edition of cotton crepe in white, adorned with a plethora of blooms and flora. Crystal buttonry enhances the youthful look as does embroidered flapper pants with  playful peekaboo piping detail.

title: Bianco Rings / LKD0772
description: WOV's signature off white aesthetic creates not just a play of texture in this broche chiffon jacket but also provides the best canvas to display the intricate hand embroidery techniques that are exclusive to the luxury retailer. From pearls to resham silk knots ,kora french bullion, rose gold dabka and glass beads, this floral geometric is a one of a kind head turning wardrobe must have.

title: Aztec Winter 2Pc Set / LKPRM24
description: This stunning, limited-edition Pakistani design, crafted from premium fabric with exquisite lace paneling and embroidery, offers a flattering silhouette and versatile style for any celebration, from Eid to formal events. It ensures effortless elegance and all-day comfort, delivered right to your door.

title: Winter Rose 2Pc Set / LKPRM19
description: Who doesn't love red roses as a gift? We do and who better to love then the one we've known our entire lives, ourselves. Gift yourself this two peice embellished outfit with exclusive in house made buttons, silken ribbon and enjoy!

title: Geranium Fields / LKD0774
description: Capturing the beauty of a floral garden in full bloom is the newest edition to WOV's hand embroidered collection, accentuated with kora french bullion, WOV's exclusive ribbon detailing, pearl, sequins, and glass beads. Embrace the beauty of this feminine embroidered jacket accentuated by a soft silken inner.

title: Morganite Beauty 2Pc Set / LKD0769
description: Just as the light of the sun accompanies streaks of soft pink in the sky, this fully embroidered jacket inspires to capture the same beauty. Hand embroidered with thoughtful detailing unique to WOV,  blending silk resham thread, glass beading and golden kora french bullion to create a masterpiece of design artistry. The graceful visage is completed by a soft mauve inner and WOV signature cig pant.
